properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 8 at 2:21PM CST until February 9 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...ACCUMULATING SNOW EXPECTED ON SUNDAY...

* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 4 inches.
The snow may become mixed with rain in the afternoon and early
evening.

* WHERE...Waukesha and Milwaukee Counties.

* WHEN...From 9 AM to 9 PM CST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Snow covered roads and limited visibility will create
difficult driving conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Be prepared to allow extra time to reach
your destination on Sunday.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TO 9 PM CST SUNDAY
